   require gtk+ sane-backends
  optional gimp '' '--disable-gimp --disable-gimp2' for GNU Image Manipulation Program plugin
  category graphic
 attribute x11
    source ftp://ftp.sane-project.org/pub/sane/xsane/xsane-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://www.xsane.org/
  estimate 400
      desc 'xsane is a gtk+ based x11 frontend for sane-backends.
It works either standalone or as a gimp plugin.
It is an alternative to xscanimage.'
